Military helicopter with 10 on board crashes in central Romania
BUCHAREST, Nov. 21 (Xinhua) -- A Puma SOCAT helicopter with some 10 military personnel onboard crashed Friday near Medias City, Romanian central county of Sibiu, local TV station reported.
The Defence Ministry has already confirmed the accident and Defence Minister Mircea Dusa was quoted as saying that 8 of the 10 onboard died in the accident.
The helicopter was heading to Cincu military base, some 45 km to the southeast of the crash site, for joint military exercises with the U.S. military.